00:17:35.160 --> 00:17:38.160
To su komarci koji prenose parazit malarije

00:17:38.160 --> 00:17:42.160
Koji zarazi našu krv kad komarac dobije besplatan obrok

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:44.160
